OL,6,FA loan shark from who repeatedly
OL,7,Fkidnapped and attacked a man to extort
OL,8,Fmoney has been jailed.
OL,10,FRichard Dawson terrorised the man and
OL,11,Fhis vulnerable mother after they
OL,12,Fbecame "trapped in a cycle of debt", a
OL,13,Fcourt heard.
OL,15,FHe forced the man into the boot of his
OL,16,Fcar on several occasions - including
OL,17,Fincidents captured on CCTV - before
OL,18,Fdriving him to cash machines to
OL,19,Fwithdraw money. On one occasion he
OL,20,Ffractured his jaw.
