OL,6,FRecorder Adrian Langdale KC described
OL,7,FDawson as "a vicious loan shark" and
OL,8,Fthat the two victims who reported him,
OL,9,Fwere the only ones "brave enough to
OL,10,Fcome forward."
OL,12,FHe said: "Any right-thinking member of
OL,13,Fsociety will be disgusted by the way
OL,14,Fyou treated human beings.
OL,16,F"You treated them as nothing more than
OL,17,Fwalking cash machines to be used,
OL,18,Fabused and attacked at will and have
OL,19,Ftheir lives destroyed and treated by
OL,20,Fyou as nothing less than human beings."
