OL,6,FFollowing sentencing, Tony Quigley,
OL,7,Fhead of the England Illegal Money
OL,8,FLending Team said a "predatory
OL,9,Fcriminal" had been removed from the
OL,10,Fstreets.
OL,12,F"This man is a ruthless and cruel
OL,13,Findividual who deliberately targeted
OL,14,Fthe most vulnerable people in the
OL,15,Fcommunity, taking everything they had
OL,16,Fand leaving them with nothing. He knew
OL,17,Fthey couldn't fight back and took
OL,18,Fadvantage of that.
